OL,3,CAsda reports temporary fuel shortages
OL,4,Cas petrol hits 150p a litre
OL,6,FAsda has reported "temporary"
OL,7,Fshortages at some pumps as the price
OL,8,Fof petrol jumped above 150p per litre
OL,9,Ffor the first time in almost two years.
OL,11,FAllan Leighton, executive chairman of
OL,12,FAsda, said the retailer has seen
OL,13,Fbumper demand from drivers in response
OL,14,Fto the volatility in prices due to the
OL,15,Fwar in the Middle East.
OL,26,@nD@SOU
