OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774696008
OL,3,CAsda reports temporary fuel shortages
OL,4,Cas petrol hits 150p a litre
OL,6,FPetrol and diesel prices have lifted
OL,7,Fsignificantly since the end of
OL,8,FFebruary after the war between US-
OL,9,FIsraeli and Iran led to disruption in
OL,10,Fthe production and supply of oil from
OL,11,Fthe Middle East.
OL,13,FFuel Industry UK, which represents the
OL,14,Ffuel sector, said the supply of petrol
OL,15,Fand diesel is "stable".
OL,26,@wD@OOUwD@VO]
