OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774696008
OL,3,CAsda reports temporary fuel shortages
OL,4,Cas petrol hits 150p a litre
OL,6,FThe Petrol Retailer Association (PRA)
OL,7,Fhas echoed this, saying that suppliers
OL,8,Fare "working hard to deliver normal
OL,9,Flevels of supply through a mix of UK
OL,10,Frefinery production and imported
OL,11,Ffuels".
OL,13,F"Industry and government remain in
OL,14,Fregular contact to monitor deliveries
OL,15,Fand stock levels in the UK as well as
OL,16,Fthe situation internationally", they
OL,17,Fadded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
