OL,3,CAsda reports temporary fuel shortages
OL,4,Cas petrol hits 150p a litre
OL,6,FThe average price of unleaded petrol
OL,7,Fhas risen by more than 17p a litre
OL,8,Fsince the end of February to 150.11p,
OL,9,Faccording to fresh RAC data.
OL,11,FLeighton, the boss of the UK's second-
OL,12,Flargest fuel retailer, stressed the
OL,13,Ftemporary shortages have only affected
OL,14,F"the odd pump" at a small number of
OL,15,Fits petrol forecourts, highlighting no
OL,16,Fforecourts have been fully short of
OL,17,Ffuel.
OL,19,FHe said: "Our fuel volumes are up
OL,20,Fquite significantly and clearly demand
OL,21,Fhas been outstripping supply.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@NO]{D@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
