OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774696008
OL,3,CAsda reports temporary fuel shortages
OL,4,Cas petrol hits 150p a litre
OL,6,F"Supply is tight and we are all trying
OL,7,Fhard on that.
OL,9,F"The issue is a temporary one, and
OL,10,Fsome could see issues when we are
OL,11,Fwaiting for delivery, and we can
OL,12,Fexpect to see that continue.
OL,14,F"The spikiness at the moment makes
OL,15,Fthis tricky for us, as spikes can lead
OL,16,Fto temporary shortages. These are
OL,17,Ftemporary and are addressed very
OL,18,Fquickly."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUvD@AOUzD@IO]
