OL,3,CAsda reports temporary fuel shortages
OL,4,Cas petrol hits 150p a litre
OL,6,FRAC head of policy Simon Williams
OL,7,Fsaid: "Petrol has now broken through
OL,8,Fthe unwelcome milestone of 150p a
OL,9,Flitre, something drivers haven't seen
OL,10,Fsince mid-May two years ago, while the
OL,11,Faverage price of diesel is now
OL,12,Fapproaching 180p at 177.68p.
OL,14,F"With the long-awaited four-day Easter
OL,15,Fweekend almost within touching
OL,16,Fdistance, the cost of getting away by
OL,17,Fcar is going to be noticeably higher
OL,18,Fthis year."
OL,26,@oD@GOUvD@AOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
