OL,3,CAsda reports temporary fuel shortages
OL,4,Cas petrol hits 150p a litre
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FLast year, around 90% of crude oil
OL,12,Frefined in the UK ` which is used to
OL,13,Fproduce petrol ` was imported, with
OL,14,Faround 1% of this imported from the
OL,15,FMiddle East, with most coming from the
OL,16,FUS and Norway.
OL,18,FAround 7% of diesel is imported from
OL,19,Fthe Middle East.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
