OL,3,CAsda reports temporary fuel shortages
OL,4,Cas petrol hits 150p a litre
OL,6,FUK refinery production of petrol, from
OL,7,Fcrude oil, exceeded demand in 2025,
OL,8,Faccording to official data.
OL,10,FThe boss also rejected claims that
OL,11,Ffuel retailers have boosted their
OL,12,Fprofits through recent price increases.
OL,14,FEarlier this month, the prime minister
OL,15,Fsaid the government would step in if
OL,16,Fretailers try "to rip off customers"
OL,17,Fthrough price gouging.
OL,19,FIn response, Mr Leighton said "no, we
OL,20,Fare not" when asked if the business
OL,21,Fwas profiteering.
OL,26,@xD@OOUxD@dO]{D@_OU|D@HO]
