OL,3,CAsda reports temporary fuel shortages
OL,4,Cas petrol hits 150p a litre
OL,6,FHe said: "Our (profit) margin will be
OL,7,Fdown as a result. It is very clear
OL,8,Fthis is not the case.
OL,10,F"People ask where the money is going
OL,11,Fand the government are getting a lot
OL,12,Fof money off the back of this."
